['chilled nahi hain?', "wo chilled hain. by the way, i'm nagesh iyer.", 'hi. nagesh iyer as in wo nagesh iyer. aap novels likhte hain na?', 'wo side business hain. main business raddi ki dukaan.', 'kya?', 'haan. meri books bookstore mein kam jyada bikti hain raddi ki dukaan mein. isiliye mein khud khol li raddi ki dukaan.', 'mein aapke wo novel khareedi thi - man, woman and therefore.', 'kaise lagi?', 'nice.', 'ye pakode kaise?', 'nice.', 'ab mein samjha aap ghar chood kar kyu aayen hain. kisi ka dil nahi tod sakte the to. sabko khus karne ki kowshis mein khud pareeshaan ho jaate ho. right? sach sach batao na ye pakoode kaise hain.', 'akal pada hota na, daane daane ke liye taras raha hota aur ye pakode kha kar jaan bacha sakta na fir bhi ye pakode nahi khaata. ye ghatiya pakode, ye kharab pakode.', 'aur meri novel?', 'ye pakode aur tumahri wo novel isme agar ek chiiz compulsory hoti na to ye pakoda khaake meri life de deta lekin tumari wo ghatiya novel life mein nahi padta. itna ghatiya novel likhi hain tumne mr nayar.', 'iyer', 'iyer. and one more thing', 'musician sings', 'jaiye jaiye aap jaiye', 'okay be happy man.', "be happy. i'm very happy.", 'good. aisa ghar pe kyu nahi karte?', 'arey nahi kar sakta na yaar. ghar pe sab mere apne and i love them aur mein hi hoon unka agony uncle.']
